<item>
            <title>[HBASE-2325] Add build hook to allow jvm args to be passed to junit test runner</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-2325</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In order to run jcarder on the unit tests, it&apos;s handy to be able to add jvm args to the junit test runner. This trivial patch adds a hook for this. Unfortunately I don&apos;t know much about maven, someone will have to help me for trunk.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
